This week there's also escalating
tensions internationally,

10:14.536 --> 10:18.096
especially between DPRK and America.

10:18.106 --> 10:19.630
Are the effects of that felt here?

10:19.640 --> 10:22.341
Is it making any difference
to the celebrations?

