Ahmed's restaurants have
been attacked several times

23:06.451 --> 23:08.709
by suicide bombers, active shooters,

23:08.719 --> 23:10.812
and vehicle-borne IEDs.

23:10.822 --> 23:13.147
But each time, he's reopened.

23:13.157 --> 23:16.016
How do you stay safe when you're
running restaurants like this?

