23:46.723 --> 23:50.992
Why is it important to open
restaurants in a city like Mogadishu?

23:59.702 --> 24:00.834
Yeah.

24:08.711 --> 24:10.202
One of the most pressing needs

24:10.212 --> 24:13.071
in a country decimated
by decades of civil war

24:13.081 --> 24:14.773
is infrastructure.

24:14.783 --> 24:16.809
We met up with a
Somali-American engineer

24:16.819 --> 24:19.077
who offered to show us his new project,

24:19.087 --> 24:20.746
a million-dollar investment.

24:20.756 --> 24:23.281
Gianna. Nice to meet you.

24:23.291 --> 24:26.159
Good! This does not look
like the rest of Mogadishu.

24:27.195 --> 24:29.121
It feels like California.

24:29.131 --> 24:31.756
You have butterflies in your garden.

24:31.766 --> 24:34.467
Sell me one of these apartments.
Tell me why I should move here.

24:35.437 --> 24:36.736
Sure.

24:41.709 --> 24:43.367
Very nice.

24:43.377 --> 24:44.844
So much natural light.

24:46.581 --> 24:48.213
How many bedrooms, you said?

24:51.786 --> 24:53.144
Wow, look at this.

24:53.154 --> 24:55.479
You got the balcony and everything.

24:55.489 --> 24:59.450
So, I gotta say, on this side,
it's amazing. You can see the ocean.

24:59.460 --> 25:01.896
But the foreground is all
bombed-out buildings.

