25:34.227 --> 25:35.651
Diaspora are building up,

25:35.661 --> 25:38.721
and now for the first time
in more than 25 years,

25:38.731 --> 25:41.091
they're creating a
functioning government.

25:41.101 --> 25:42.725
In February, the parliament elected

25:42.735 --> 25:44.694
a Somali-American as president,

25:44.704 --> 25:46.128
in a historic vote.

25:46.138 --> 25:47.494
We visited Villa Somalia,

25:47.505 --> 25:48.983
their version of the White House,

25:48.994 --> 25:51.968
as the president announced
the 26 new ministers.

