27:41.034 --> 27:44.109
Ilwad Elman is a
27-year-old Somali-Canadian

27:44.119 --> 27:45.944
who left her safe life in Ottawa

27:45.954 --> 27:49.281
to deradicalize Al-Shabaab
child soldiers.

27:49.291 --> 27:52.451
These safe houses,
these are for children

27:52.461 --> 27:53.619
that are still under threat.

27:53.629 --> 27:57.122
Children that have been forcibly
recruited into Al-Shabaab,

27:57.132 --> 27:59.157
managed to escape,

27:59.167 --> 28:02.928
were then put into detention for being
forcibly recruited into Al-Shabaab,

28:02.938 --> 28:06.464
and then used by government
security forces as informants.

28:06.474 --> 28:09.801
But we believe that children
can become children again

28:09.811 --> 28:13.037
if they are taken out of
these militarized contexts.

28:13.047 --> 28:14.071
Mm-hmm.

28:14.081 --> 28:17.975
And I've seen that hundreds
of times over again.

28:17.985 --> 28:20.177
Ilwad does extremely dangerous work

28:20.187 --> 28:23.313
and is the boldest example
of diaspora coming back.

28:23.323 --> 28:25.816
In fact, her father paid with his life

28:25.826 --> 28:27.651
for doing the same type of work.

28:27.661 --> 28:29.887
So, my dad and my mom were both...

28:29.897 --> 28:31.421
ardent human rights activists.

28:31.431 --> 28:34.891
And... when the war started to escalate,

28:34.901 --> 28:37.561
my mom and dad made a
decision that she would leave

28:37.571 --> 28:40.297
with me and my sisters,
and my dad would stay behind.

28:40.307 --> 28:43.433
I went back, just to understand
what the context was like,

28:43.443 --> 28:46.169
and as soon as I did,
one month turned to three months,

28:46.179 --> 28:48.838
turned to one year,
and now I'm here for seven years.

28:53.653 --> 28:55.245
In order to rebuild,

28:55.255 --> 28:58.314
there needs to be an investment

28:58.324 --> 29:00.049
in the young people.

29:00.059 --> 29:01.651
By investing in young people,

29:01.661 --> 29:03.920
we will not have...

29:03.930 --> 29:05.221
hundreds of people taking on

29:05.231 --> 29:06.922
the Mediterranean Sea every single year,

29:06.932 --> 29:08.491
trying to think that the only way

29:08.501 --> 29:10.526
for a good life is outside of Somalia.

29:10.536 --> 29:13.329
I want to show them the
opportunities that are here.

29:13.339 --> 29:16.507
And it just starts with
actually giving someone hope.

